Samsung Tizen Coding Challenge - Tizen movie app
Primary Used: Javascript, C, HTML, CSS
The following requirements were met
- 1 central page with two buttons.
- 1 tab titled “Now Playing”
- 1 tab titled “Upcoming movies”
- Each button shows a vertical of movies according to the button selected
 Each movie item has:
   - Movie name
   - Movie vote average (populatity)
   - Movie Detail page:
     On clicking movie in the list goes to movie detail page
   - Movie details page has movie title, poster, genre, release date, overview
Following extra features were implemented
-Showing the movie genres in each movie item
- Showing 1 associated image in the movie detail page
- Pagination is handled
- Error handling (eg. No internet, service app launch error, port errors)


  
